title: Passing the Test of the Symbolic World Facebook Group
description: A little banter before the official start of my @Jonathan Pageau  @Paul VanderKlay  conversation. We go over how easy it is to join Paul's Bridges of Meaning discord group, and how not easy it is to join Jonathan's Symbolic World Facebook group (not run by either guy but they are the respective patriarch of each)
